			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Debug book: add Lae'Zel to your party\r\nDebug book: go to the Plains, near the gith chokepoint\r\nteleport -130, 542\r\nSkip through that dialogue\r\nApproach the gith\r\nTake a branch through the gith chokepoint dialogue that will end in hostility, so fail a check or attack them.\r\nReCon: killcombat\r\nLae'Zel should speak to you, triggering GLO_GithChokepoint_WRD_Laezel."
				},
